  "title": "Displaying values with interpolation",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/interpolation.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"displaying-values-with-interpolation\">Displaying values with interpolation<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#displaying-values-with-interpolation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"使用插值语法显示值\">使用插值语法显示值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#使用插值语法显示值\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"前提条件\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#前提条件\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">Basics of components</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">组件基础</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">Basics of templates</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">模板基础</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">Binding syntax</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">绑定语法</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!--todo: needs a level 2 heading for info below -->\n<p>Interpolation refers to embedding expressions into marked up text. By default, interpolation uses the double curly braces <code>{{</code> and <code>}}</code> as delimiters.</p>\n<p>插值是指将表达式嵌入到被标记的文本中。默认情况下，插值使用双花括号 <code>{{</code> 和 <code>}}</code> 作为定界符。</p>\n<p>To illustrate how interpolation works, consider an Angular component that contains a <code>currentCustomer</code> variable:</p>\n<p>为了说明插值的工作原理，请考虑一个包含 <code>currentCustomer</code> 变量的 Angular 组件：</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.ts\" region=\"customer\">\ncurrentCustomer = 'Maria';\n\n</code-example>\n<p>Use interpolation to display the value of this variable in the corresponding component template:</p>\n<p>可以用插值在相应的组件模板中显示此变量的值：</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"interpolation-example1\">\n&#x3C;h3>Current customer: {{ currentCustomer }}&#x3C;/h3>\n\n</code-example>\n<p>Angular replaces <code>currentCustomer</code> with the string value of the corresponding component property. In this case, the value is <code>Maria</code>.</p>\n<p>Angular 会用相应组件属性的字符串值替换掉 <code>currentCustomer</code>。在这里，它的值是 <code>Maria</code>。</p>\n<p>In the following example, Angular evaluates the <code>title</code> and <code>itemImageUrl</code> properties to display some title text and an image.</p>\n<p>在以下示例中，Angular 会求出 <code>title</code> 和 <code>itemImageUrl</code> 属性的值，以显示一些标题文本和图像。</p>\n<code-example path=\"interpolation/src/app/app.component.html\" region=\"component-property\">\n&#x3C;p>{{title}}&#x3C;/p>\n&#x3C;div>&#x3C;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> alt=\"item\" src=\"{{itemImageUrl}}\">&#x3C;/div>\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\">What's Next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"下一步呢\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/interpolation#下一步呢\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">Property binding</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">property 绑定</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">Event binding</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件绑定</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 4/14/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/template-overview\n - guide/template-statements\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/user-input\n - tutorial/toh-pt5\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/interpolation#displaying-values-with-interpolation\n - guide/interpolation#prerequisites\n - guide/interpolation#whats-next\n - guide/interpolation#下一步呢\n - guide/interpolation#使用插值语法显示值\n - guide/interpolation#前提条件\n - guide/property-binding\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/interpolation.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
